## Market Validation: AI in Research Survey Findings

- **24% spend 21-30% of time on admin tasks** (largest segment)
- **Combined 44.6% spend 21-40% of time on admin** vs actual research
- **Top time consumers**: Data entry, report generation, scheduling, communication
- **Only 7.2% spend less than 10% on admin tasks**

**Strategic Validation**: Our "automate up to 80% of workflow" positioning directly addresses the market's #1 pain point.

#### **2. AI Adoption Readiness Confirms Market Timing**
- **76.9% want AI-based method selection tools** - validates our platform approach

**Strategic Validation**: High interest across all our core platform capabilities demonstrates market readiness.

**Strategic Validation**: Our "reduce research lifecycle from months to days" directly addresses duration concerns.
